{"tid":1888472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【預言】三年內，罷工醫護將有25%人離職，留低嘅都唔會有前途。","createTime":"2020-02-20T08:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T23:02:29.000Z","uid":78492,"like":13,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6f9e2e02d541a14e20fafa6f0eec8ad53728f3bd","tid":1888472,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"中聯辦吹雞搞罷工醫護，睇黎實死無生，RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n參加咗工會，簽署罷工而最終無罷工仲好落力返工但又呻無裝備既醫護，將會吹捧成救港英雄，升職加人工，榮華富貴，享之不盡。<br />\n至於帶頭搞工會既，不論界別，死硬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非立法會功能組別都控制到，不過預期選舉前會湧現海量（功能組別無用論）嘅白票撚"},{"pid":"f03f83d38d40f5029e430715fe52349ce2842454","tid":1888472,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"有錢都唔使去HA啦<br />\n<br />\n由得d人慢慢留HA醫d廢老基層新移民啦"},{"pid":"cd421dc8bbab89f58043ba721b0b4ba509a53093","tid":1888472,"uid":32683,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:50:48.000Z","msg":"好笑 護士長都係五萬幾起薪 再高d經理都係七萬幾起薪 何來榮華富貴享之不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae29b7cb301690523d168b92e7a339457cd5c701","tid":1888472,"uid":148,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"好撚煩 剩係識屌人白票撚<br />\n有無諗過呢個世界係有唔同光譜<br />\n有班本土派、獨派本身根本就唔會玩功能組別<br />\n大家路線唔同有分歧好撚正常<br />\n可唔可以唔好屌呢班人白票撚先<br />\n有無企過喺佢地光譜諗過？"},{"pid":"40888bdfb0c4b988100b7567395f6a6fec220aa2","tid":1888472,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"估唔到我估得太過保守<br />\n原來係咁快同係全炒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6529789fc79e0d13e5120dc6317e1afe739c10","tid":1888472,"uid":216441,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHxWiaL.gif\" data-thumbnail-